{"tid":776183,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 我係咪激嬲咗個補習老師","createTime":"2018-08-11T19:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T09:17:15.000Z","uid":136116,"like":1,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e073cbb15692af489a1db9dce830d6e38697bcce","tid":776183,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:33:14.000Z","msg":"話說小妹今日派咗啲成績出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個補習老師一向都好緊張我啲成績<br />\n所以成績派咗冇幾耐佢就問我啲成績點<br />\n:我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n:你今日啲成績點？<br />\n:中文差兩分半<br />\n:英文呢？<br />\n:都係差兩分半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n:(以為我差兩分半先合格)咁你咪死得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n:唔會啊，因為我其實冇講過話我唔合格 我之係差兩分半先到X字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢就話我玩佢，係度鬧我，我就想知我咁樣算唔算玩佢？又或者呢個玩笑會唔會太過分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係小妹今次個玩笑係係唔適當嘅場合出現？係咪我錯？希望各位大大可以解答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw小妹都識咗佢好耐 所以都幾frd 但就唔知佢會因為呢啲事就嬲咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7812120ba4c3d5097caa76e69947108fdc34889d","tid":776183,"uid":197135,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:35:11.000Z","msg":"佢覺得你唔尊重佢<br />\n咁你又係幼稚左啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3def19b63228a40861dd1717691612199ba460","tid":776183,"uid":136116,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"7812120ba4c3d5097caa76e69947108fdc34889d","tid":776183,"uid":197135,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:35:11.000Z","msg":"佢覺得你唔尊重佢<br />\n咁你又係幼稚左啲既<img sr